This document presents a conceptual engineering assessment.

Absolute torque (N·m), tractive force (N), power (kW), acceleration (m/s²),
and top speed cannot be calculated without defining:

• EM220 continuous and peak power
• Motor speed range (rpm)
• Gear reduction ratio
• Hydraulic operating pressure
• Actuator piston geometry
• Wheel radius
• Tire-road friction coefficient
• Vehicle mass
• Aerodynamic drag characteristics

